  <header class="main-hd">
    <h3 class="title">
      <a href="https://book.douban.com/review/2815655/" class="title-link">南明皇帝的稱呼</a>
      <div class="toggle_review right">        <a href="javascript:;" id="toggle-2815655"class="indicator unfold j" title="展开全文">        </a>
      </div>
    </h3>
    

<div class="header-more">
    <a class="author-avatar" href="https://www.douban.com/people/1084895/"><img width="48" height="48" src="https://img3.doubanio.com/icon/u1084895-5.jpg"></a>
    <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/1084895/" class="author">
      <span property="v:reviewer">谷子</span>
    </a>    <span property="v:rating" class="allstar40 main-title-rating" title="推荐"></span>
  <span property="v:dtreviewed" content="2009-12-03"
      class="main-meta">2009-12-03 10:20:32</span>
</div>

  </header>

        <div class="main-bd">
          <div id="review_2815655_short" class="review-short">
            <div class="short-content">
                  晚明史一書是一部不錯的書。不過，在敘述南明弘光部份有點混亂（比如，南北偽太子案，南方太子絕對是偽太子，而被滿清殺害的北方太子，絕對是眞太子，孟森先生文章斷之甚確，但此書卻寫的模模糊糊），而且，稱即位后的弘光皇帝為福王，也不甚妥當。全書稱崇禎帝爲思宗，那麼對...

                    <a class="pl" href="https://book.douban.com/review/2815655/#comments">(1回应)</a>
                  <div class="more-info pl clearfix">
                    <span class="left">3有用 / 3没用</span>
                  </div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div id="review_2815655_full" class="hidden">
            <div id="review_2815655_full_content" class="full-content"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
    </div>
  </div>





</div>










            <p class="pl" align="right">
                &gt;
                <a href="reviews">
                    更多书评4篇
                </a>
